How to integrate payment Gateway
1)Choose a payment gateway(Remita)
2)Register on the platform and optain API keys
3)Add dependencies in your pom.xml
4)Configure API leys
5)Store API keys securely
6)Implement payment end point
7)Create controller to handle payment request
8)Test the payment in test mode befoe switching to live mode

